8.c Misconduct includes without limitation:
8.c.i habitual absence from work or absence from service without prior notice in writing or
without sufficient cause for ten days or more;
8.c.ii causing damage to the property of the Company;
8.c.iii continued discharge of work functions in a manner which does not meet the standards
reasonably expected by the Company from you;
8.c.iv engaging in any conduct amounting to sexual harassment as defined under the
Company’s policies; or
8.c.v breach of the GOC Code of Conduct, any policy contained in the Company’s intranet site,
or any other policy communicated to employees.

